@startuml l1_evaluation
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam defaultFontName "Segoe UI"
skinparam defaultFontSize 11
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam roundCorner 10
skinparam activityDiamondBackgroundColor #FFF9C4

title **Level 1 — Evaluation Process**

start

:Generic Agent produces\nconsulting report;
note right
  Report includes self-evaluation
  (agent assesses its own work)
end note

:Self-evaluation embedded\nin report output;

partition "Standalone Evaluator (Separate Service)" #FFFDE7 {
  :Submit report to\nEvaluator service;
  :Evaluator (gemini-2.5-flash)\nscores on 6-criterion rubric;
  note right
    **Criteria (1-10 each):**
    * Completeness
    * Accuracy
    * Coherence
    * Structure
    * Actionability
    * Critical Depth
  end note
  :Produce Evaluation\nScorecard JSON;
}

:Compare self-evaluation\nvs evaluator scores;
note right
  **Key comparison:**
  How well does a single
  unspecialized agent assess
  its own quality?
end note

stop

note bottom
  **Level 1 Evaluation:**
  * Self-evaluation (embedded in report)
  * External evaluation (standalone Evaluator service)
  * No revision capability — single pass only
  * Serves as baseline for cross-level comparison
end note

@enduml
